The privacy policy describes the procedures and policies on the collection and use
of information provided by You (User) of the application. After downloading the application, users are required to provide their Full Name, Email Address and Password to authenticate the user to use the application. 

Definitions
Account - this means a unique account created for the user to access or use the application.
Application - this means the software program/application provided by KJ Radio
The application can be downloaded by the You/User on your Devices using the iPhone Operating System and Android Operating System.

Types of Data Collected
Personal Data
To use the application, You/User must provide us with certain information that personally identifies You.

These information include:
1. Full Name
2. Email Address

Aside the above mentioned information, we also ask users to provide with feedback when filling out the contact us form on the contact us page. The information required are:
1. Title of Subject
3. Details of Message

Users can also delete their user account at the Profiles Page.
The information provided will help KJ Radio provide better services to its users.
